JSCom Plugin basic format :

Function Network Control

	Input: {form}
		Name
		Login SIP URI
		Password

Function Call :

	Call Info :

		Input a contact {form}
        Dialling pad {Selection buttons}
        Input call type : Audio/Video? {selection button}

	Call state : {Automatic selection}

		Call Dialling
		Call Incoming
		Call Accepted/Answering
		Call Connected

	Session Control : {Selection button}

		Cancel
		Reject
		Answer
		Answer with video
		//Hold
		Hangup
		Active 

Function chat :

	Input Destination {form}

	Chat error : No contact specified

Function error :

	Error Display : {Automatic Selection}

		Enable Javascript error
		Enable WebRTC - Mozilla error
		Google chrome update error
		Error in JsCommunicator configuration
		Error in user agent initialization
		SIP Registration failure
		Hardware error : microphone/webcam

Function WebSocket :

	Websocket : connected/not {selection button}

	SIP registration : 

		registered/not {selection button}
		deregister/not {selection button}

Function VideoCall :

	Remote view {selection button}
	Self view/hide {selection button}






        
        



